description: Step into a space where every detail—from the sophisticated furnishings to the designer fixtures—has been meticulously curated. Echelon Residences in Boston exemplify luxury urban living, blending contemporary elegance, comfort, and world-class amenities. Start your mornings with stunning views of Boston Harbor, sipping coffee by your custom glass Napoleon fireplace. For wine enthusiasts, the built-in EuroCave wine fridge keeps your collection perfectly chilled. Designed with entertaining in mind, the layout features an open-concept living area with wide oak plank flooring and an oversized kitchen island, separating the two bedrooms for added privacy. The primary bathroom includes a state-of-the-art Japanese toilet, adding an extra touch of indulgence. Whether hosting a gathering or enjoying a quiet evening in, this home is both welcoming and impressive. Valet parking and a private storage unit complete the ease of city living.
